# .gitleaksignore — allowlist for gitleaks false positives.
# Each line is a SHA256 fingerprint of a finding to suppress.
# Generate with: gitleaks detect --staged --report-format json | jq '.[].Fingerprint'
#
# ADAPT: add fingerprints for legitimate test fixtures, example keys, etc.
# Format: <sha256-fingerprint>
#
# Example (never commit real keys — this suppresses known-safe test vectors):
# 5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99a5b5d0e5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb
